[✈️ABOUT THIS DOCUMENT✈️]
See main.pdf for the tutorial for how to use VICON positioning system with a Pixhawk6C. This paper is originally aim towards AVDC MSc students in Cranfield for their GDP project, but I will release this to ArduPilot forum as I have recieved feedback that it is useful.  

[⚠️DISCLAIMER⚠️]
This document is concise so that you can get your drone to connect to Vicon. There exists many different ways to connect to Vicon (Writing your own SDK), but for your project, this should be more than okay! 


[✒️EDITING✒️]
If there exists a certain part of the doucumentation/typo which you think could have been explained better, please fork this depositionary and request to push! 

This document is written in LaTeX. The main.tex file is the one you can edit. Bibliography is in the "bibliography.bib" file. All images are located within the \Images folder.


